{"tid":1098073,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"一句講晒，鄭秀文定容祖兒演唱會？","createTime":"2019-04-08T21:30:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T12:24:59.000Z","uid":90315,"like":20,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"190ffd3d4e1869552892ff7b5d31c8fa07a23b89","tid":1098073,"uid":90315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T21:30:34.000Z","msg":"鄭秀文<br />\n<br />\n老<br />\n平<br />\n跳舞似神打<br />\n硬sell福音<br />\n歌要降key<br />\n把聲唔惦，唱多幾場就聲沙，高音避得就避<br />\n所以會有嘉賓抖氣位，但嘉賓有時會好騎尼，撞手神<br />\n場數較少，四面台<br />\n選曲偏保守，翻唱多數難聽<br />\n氣氛較容好<br />\n快歌多hit歌<br />\n近年無邊首hit<br />\n短期內話唔會再開<br />\n<br />\n容祖兒<br />\n<br />\n仲叫後生，有氣有力<br />\n平<br />\n歌衫較靚，樣較醜<br />\n多數原key, 唱唔洗點擔心<br />\n但後面場數都多數聲沙<br />\n多數無嘉賓<br />\n跳舞好睇<br />\n場數多，？面台<br />\n選曲變化較大，希望無黃偉文攪亂檔<br />\n氣氛比較差<br />\n講野有時唔到位致氣氛尷尬<br />\n近年都少左hit歌，上年叫有首心之科學<br />\n唔唱歌唔知做得d乜，所以將來仲有大把機會"},{"pid":"c28fb061e76717619401a275ed6dcdf285cbe76e","tid":1098073,"uid":24378,"like":16,"dislike":15,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T23:56:43.000Z","msg":"兩邊都唔撚睇，拎啲錢嚟支持下新一代好過"},{"pid":"10e23f50e276bfaa2a59909cf5415a7aac8f1435","tid":1098073,"uid":90315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T01:59:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9cae193aabb8ea024ec344aca7310879f16452","tid":1098073,"uid":218626,"like":8,"dislike":7,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T02:02:05.000Z","msg":"睇軒算la"},{"pid":"4f73d8935378023781602fc654f0a4aa18f2e67c","tid":1098073,"uid":26773,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T04:02:56.000Z","msg":"Joey live 》 sammi"},{"pid":"f6cee74bc2e9f0af3eda7d00be74d03dbf3432d9","tid":1098073,"uid":196397,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"容姨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\